/li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThird century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/236_AC\" title=\"236 AC\">236</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/262_AC\" title=\"262 AC\">262</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/297_AC\" title=\"297 AC\">297</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n<b>Year 61 After the Conquest</b> (<b>61 AC</b>) is a year in the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Westerosi calendar</a>, the 61st after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon</a>'s crowning in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> that maesters and educated people use as a reference to date the years.\n</p><p>In 61 AC King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I</a> joined lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a> and five hundred stormlanders in an assault at the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Mountains\" title=\"Red Mountains\">Red Mountains</a> to hunt down the <a href=\"/index.php/Vulture_King_(Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Vulture King (Jaehaerys I)\">Vulture King</a>, who was aided by Rogar's brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Borys_Baratheon\" title=\"Borys Baratheon\">Borys</a>. Both outlaws were slain in less than half a year, in the conflict that would be known as \"Lord Rogar's War\" or the \"Third Dornish War\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:212px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Death_of_Borros_Baratheon_by_Ivelin_Trifonov_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Death_of_Borros_Baratheon_by_Ivelin_Trifonov_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/210px-Death_of_Borros_Baratheon_by_Ivelin_Trifonov_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"279\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Death_of_Borros_Baratheon_by_Ivelin_Trifonov_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/315px-Death_of_Borros_Baratheon_by_Ivelin_Trifonov_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Death_of_Borros_Baratheon_by_Ivelin_Trifonov_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/420px-Death_of_Borros_Baratheon_by_Ivelin_Trifonov_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Death_of_Borros_Baratheon_by_Ivelin_Trifonov_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jaehaerys I Targaryen kills Borys Baratheon by Ivelin Trifonov for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Births\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Births</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Deaths\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Deaths</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Titles_and_Appointments\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Titles and Appointments</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=61_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a> delivers his daughter <a href=\"/index.php/Jocelyn_Baratheon\" title=\"Jocelyn Baratheon\">Jocelyn Baratheon</a> and two daughters of his brother <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnal_Baratheon\" title=\"Ronnal Baratheon\">Ronnal</a> at the court as wards of the kings.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Births\">Births</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=61_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Births\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Elys_Arryn\" title=\"Elys Arryn\">Elys Arryn</a>, daughter of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Arryn\" title=\"Rodrik Arryn\">Rodrik Arryn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Deaths\">Deaths</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=61_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Deaths\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Borys_Baratheon\" title=\"Borys Baratheon\">Borys Baratheon</a> slain in single combat with <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The second <a href=\"/index.php/Vulture_King_(Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Vulture King (Jaehaerys I)\">Vulture King</a>, cut down by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_Towers\" title=\"Maegor Towers\">Maegor Towers</a>, last of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Towers_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"House Towers of Harrenhal\">House Towers</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Titles_and_Appointments\">Titles and Appointments</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=61_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Titles and Appointments\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>After the extinction of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Towers_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"House Towers of Harrenhal\">House Towers</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a> becomes the ruler of Harrenhal. She late Maegor's servants to her own household.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=61_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne: Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the calculation for: <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued)#Elys_Arryn\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued)\">Elys Arryn</a></i></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404221642\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.042 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.045 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1178/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 15898/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 23101/2097152 bytes\n